properties.description: Silver 8-Burner Liquid Propane Gas Grill
properties.title: Royal Gourmet Silver 8-Burner Liquid Propane Gas Grill
properties.full_description: Put aside those small grills, only the BBQ king grill can hold your necessity for big events! With Royal Gourmet® GB8000 event 8-burner BBQ propane gas grill, there’s no activity that you can’t reach, be it a picnic, tailgate party, or poolside feast. This versatile grill features a very large cooking area of 969 sq. Inches. The grates come from porcelain wiring material with food-grade treatment. 8 Stainless steel tube burners boast an overall 104,000 BTUs output; so, no worries about its power supply! Each of two different oil management systems includes a draw-out drip tray and a removable grease cup for fast and convenient cleanup. The heavy-duty, large-capacity open cart facilitates enough storage space. Please note that LP tank will be secured on either side of the grill due to double gas support systems, which are designed for creating individual grilling zones. Afraid of storage issue? No problem, folding down side tables will help make it fit in your limited storage room, and 4 casters enable its free movement. This liquid propane grill is primed for even the biggest parties and can handle more than 60 burgers or 120 hot dogs at once. Erect wind deflectors around the cooking area, and extend side tables to start grilling up some gorgeous burgers, pancakes or sandwiches for your mouth-watering guests.

properties.title: Royal Gourmet Silver 5-Burner Liquid Propane Gas Grill with 1 Side Burner
properties.full_description: Spend more time with parents, kids and your beloved one around Royal Gourmet® classic 6-burner stainless steel LP gas grill in your backyard! The grill features a total of 71,000 BTUs cooking power over 5 stainless steel tube burners (10,000 BTUs each), a U-shape searing burner (12,000 BTUs), and a lidded side burner (9,000 BTUs). The searing burner is powerful enough to lock in juices on any fine cut of meat, and the lidded side burner (9,000 BTU) is a perfect match for side dishes. Porcelain-enameled cooking grates distributes heat evenly across the generous cooking area of 598 sq. Inches area. The swing-away warming rack offers a secondary cooking area of 199 sq. Inches. Electronic ignition system provides quick start-up with a simple push. Efficient grease management system facilitates easy and effortless clean-up. The double-layer lid ensures excellent heat retention. LP tank and other large grill necessities can be stored in the bottom cabinet.
